，班人未訓醒定坐左幾年呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a45933abf09d3e0435fa8799fcfde428aef85c3","tid":1169440,"uid":56390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"文匯報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}